Open config/config.conf file and set the important variables.

cd into the ccManager directory and execute "./ccManager.sh" without the quotes.
	
DO NOT run ccMiner, this program runs the miner for you.
	
If you want email alerts, you must configure mailutils - see http://www.ubuntututorials.com/send-email-command-line-ubuntu/
	
visit http://www.coindiscussion.co.uk/forum/viewtopic.php?f=46&t=295 for support
	
-String
